      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezekiel 27:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the plural of the passive participial is found, \"made of cedar,\" not with A. Schultens, \"",
